title: Ebro In The Morning - The New Kanye Documentary Is Here
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/18/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the new Kanye Documentary, Matt Stafford's unfortunate fumble, and much more. 

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems, to learn some Black Facts, and the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
